org.archive.wayback.accesscontrol

Interface ExclusionFilterFactory

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContextExclusionFilterFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompositeExclusionFilterFactory, CustomPolicyOracleFilterFactory, OracleExclusionFilterFactory, OraclePolicyService, RedisRobotExclusionFilterFactory, RemoteExclusionFilterFactory, RobotExclusionFilterFactory, StaticListExclusionFilterFactory, StaticMapExclusionFilterFactory

    public interface ExclusionFilterFactory
    The factory for ExclusionFilter object. Life cycle of ExclusionFilter is one replay session request. This interface is used for creating an ExclusionFilter instance for each replay session.

    Migrating to more flexible and easier-to-implement ContextExclusionFilterFactory. Please consider implementing it instead.
